curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/485' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM5018", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM5018 is a quad, SPDT (single-pole/double-  throw), TTL/CMOS compatible analog switch. It  operates from a 1.8V to 5.5V single power supply.  The SGM5018 features high-speed, low on-resistance,  low voltage and high bandwidth. The high performances  make it very suitable for multiple applications, such as  portable equipment, audio and video signal routing, etc.  Low power consumption is also one of the important  reasons that make it a good choice.  The SGM5018 is available in a Green TSSOP-16  package. It operates over an ambient temperature  range of -40℃ to +85℃.  "}'
